Make Me A Video Game!
I the brave and smart Dan have surfedBill's red sister and plan to steal her green glasses!
What are a moose and backpacking vole to do? Before you can help Beth, you'll have to collect the blue apes and hot grapes that open up the 7 worlds connected to A Bill Lair. There are 2 hats and 8 gloves in the game, along with hundreds of other goodies for you to find.